Uni Seoul, LiteStore plan 25 stores in one year, 500 across India in 5 yrs

Korean-inspired lifestyle brand Uni Seoul has partnered with Bengaluru-based retail start-up LiteStore to roll out 25 offline stores across India over the next year, as part of its plan to open 500 stores in five years.
